public class SqlTimeBasedHades

implements SqlTimeBasedHadesMBean

Hades whose monitor is of type SqlTimeBasedMonitorImpl.

This class extends Hades simply by implementing jmx operations defined in SqlTimeBasedHadesMBean. These operations are specific to sql time measuring done by the associated SqlTimeBasedMonitor.
